    <p>Com­ple­ment the ro­bust Thai flavours of your take­away or­der from Blue Jas­mine with some of con­fec­tionery Chalk Farm’s most pop­u­lar Asian-in­spired cakes such as Gula Me­laka Chif­fon.</p>
    <p>Un­til De­cem­ber, Blue Jas­mine will fea­ture a dif­fer­ent cake flavour each month. Spend at least $180 on a sin­gle or­der ($250 in De­cem­ber) at the restau­rant’s e-store and get a com­pli­men­tary cake. Or­ders must be made at least three days in ad­vance. Avail­able for pickup at Park Ho­tel Far­rer Park’s main en­trance drive­way or de­liv­ery ($15).</p>
    <p>WHERE: 10 Far­rer Park Sta­tion Road WHEN: Till De­cem­ber, 11am to 9pm daily TEL: 6824-8851 INFO: Or­der at blue-jas­mine-sin­ga­pore. myshopify.com</p>


